            {/* ── CONCLUSION ── */}
            <section style={{ padding: "64px 0" }}>
              <Chapter label="Looking Forward" id="sec-conclusion" />

              <H2>From Gatekeeping to Guiding</H2>

              <P>Rethinking data isn't just a technical upgrade — it's a moral and economic one. By moving from interrogative, compliance-driven systems to relational, mobile, and purpose-aligned data practices, we can reduce waste, strengthen dignity, and dramatically improve outcomes.</P>

              <Quote>Data mobility helps us stop gatekeeping and start guiding. It ensures that vulnerable people don't have to prove they're worthy of help at every turn — they just get helped.</Quote>

              <P>That's a better deal for everyone: the clients, caseworkers, funders, and society. Doing good with data is a social good.</P>
            </section>

